formula: a(n) ~ n! / ((Pi/(2*(1+r)*log(1+r)) + log(1+r)/sqrt(1+r^2)) * r^(n+1)), where r = -0.865492354980428358034918717204144097599568833... is the root of the equation arcsinh(r)*log(1+r) = Pi/2. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Feb 02 2015
author: Patrick Demichel (patrick.demichel(AT)hp.com)
